\\\\ Control flow in Sigi

\\\\ If-else: { then_ops ; else_ops }
\\\\ Condition is popped from stack before block

!1 { "condition was true\n" ; "condition was false\n" }

!0 { "condition was true\n" ; "condition was false\n" }

\\\\ Comparisons
!3 !5 < |        \\\\ 1 (3 < 5 is true)
!5 !3 > |        \\\\ 1 (5 > 3 is true)
!3 !3 = |        \\\\ 1 (3 == 3 is true)
!0 ~ |           \\\\ 1 (NOT 0 is true)
!5 ~ |           \\\\ 0 (NOT 5 is false)
